originalText.text: We knew of Jiali through another friend who’s worked with her before. Jiali and her team are wonderful and easy to work with. They were generous with their time and help during every step of our buying process. We’ve visited a potential place multiple times and had multiple discussions before and during negotiations, and Jiali was always patient and welcoming. She has so many references for different contacts that we needed such as mortgage lender, attorney, mover, cleaner, everyone! She and her team were very helpful outside of the purchasing process as well, as we needed to find a new tenant for the previous place, and also helped mediate conversations as a neutral third party. We greatly appreciate Jiali and her team and highly recommend!

originalText.text:
As a first-time homebuyer, I’m so grateful to have Jiali and Coco as my real estate agents to help me navigate through the whole buying process which could have been stressful and confusing.

I’m very impressed by their professionalism, patience, and kindness. They were communicative and responsive to ensure that all my questions were answered. Additionally, they genuinely cared and wanted to secure the best deal for me.

Even after closing, they went the extra mile to follow up with me on moving and all other questions that I had. Highly recommend!

Her deep knowledge of the real estate market and keen eye for detail ensured that I found the perfect apartment that met all my requirements. She patiently answered all my questions and concerns, guiding me through every step of the buying process with unwavering patience.

I greatly appreciated JIali's prompt communication and willingness to go the extra mile to accommodate my schedule. Her negotiation skills also proved to be invaluable, resulting in a deal that exceeded my expectations.

I wholeheartedly recommend Jiali to anyone in search of a dedicated, trustworthy, and highly effective professional in the real estate industry.
